    "description": "Gold Award, Creativity International 48th Print & Packaging Design Competition\nHOW International Design Awards 2019 (Listed as #16; alphabetical)\n\nI was selected to be on the creative team to brand Temple University Department of Advertising's Senior Showcase (Spring 2017), an annual opportunity for students to present their portfolios to over 300 industry professionals. We developed the \"Hunt Is On\" concept to represent the job \"hunt\" both graduates and employers embark on in a competitive environment. We collaborated to design and illustrate an event logo, invitation suite, custom stamps, event signage, social media content, and a website.\n\nArt Director / Kathy Mueller\nGraphic Designers / Robin Goffman, Samantha Hilty, Suzanne Huang",
